name: Teleport

description: Mudhole? Slimy? My home this is!

description: To answer power with power, the Jedi way this is not. In this war, a danger there is, of losing who we are.

name: Bottle of strength
description: Feel the force!

name: Travel the world
description: Adventure. Excitement. A Jedi craves not these things.

description: Strong is Vader. Mind what you have learned. Save you it can.

description: At an end your rule is, and not short enough it was!

name: Talk to animals
description: Pain, suffering, death I feel. Something terrible has happened. Young Skywalker is in pain. Terrible pain

name: Early retirement
description: Use your feelings, Obi-Wan, and find him you will.

name: Bottle of calm
description: Again, feel the force!

name: Fly
description: Once you start down the dark path, forever will it dominate your destiny, consume you it will.

name: Be invisible
description: Size matters not. Look at me. Judge me by my size, do you? Hmm? Hmm. And well you should not. For my ally is the Force, and a powerful ally it is. Life creates it, makes it grow. Its energy surrounds us and binds us. Luminous beings are we, not this crude matter. You must feel the Force around you; here, between you, me, the tree, the rock, everywhere, yes. Even between the land and the ship.

name: Botte of love
description: Do. Or do not. There is no try.

name: Bottle of courage
description: Like fire across the galaxy the Clone Wars spread. In league with the wicked Count Dooku, more and more planets slip. Against this threat, upon the Jedi Knights falls the duty to lead the newly formed army of the Republic. And as the heat of war grows, so, to, grows the prowess of one most gifted student of the Force.

name: Bottle of envy
description: Not if anything to say about it I have

name: Bottle of motivation
description: Adies Yoda loves.
